{"tid":1331472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(逃亡台灣）組織協防部隊的可能性","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T05:04:32.000Z","uid":51200,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adfb6f4083e278b94004506ab33c2b228ef0629e","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"香港嘅情況越嚟越恐怖<br />\n逃亡去外國同台灣嘅人只會越來越多<br />\n好易會令到當地人反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家移民台灣<br />\n最普遍嘅條件係百幾萬港幣<br />\n但好多逃亡嘅後生仔應該都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，台灣兵源不足<br />\n後生仔又唔願意去當兵（辛苦同危險）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長遠幾十年嘅大方向來講<br />\n我覺得要說服台灣政府更改港人移民條件<br />\n加入兵役移民<br />\n重新組編香港華人軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗舒緩台灣國防壓力，亦都比冇乜錢嘅香港後生仔有個走到嘅地方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437b99559940adc769358a1dfe77d17d5b0092cb","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5412a46b819e167a6c8be848e8e4b5169bbae8","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00605b05cfc7bee5b5937449ed7be49a13d00853","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389f09006b96bef554d05a370e1904372350ea9d","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3decbdcb7ce8f0e0a9929cc8acb1931b60c39e","tid":1331472,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}